sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Browser / React :3000
    participant API as FastAPI :8000
    participant DB as MongoDB :27017
    participant ML as Inference Scheduler

    Note over ML,DB: Background — runs every 5 minutes
    ML->>DB: Read realtime_prices — last 60 rows as seed data
    ML->>ML: LSTM forward pass — 7-day price and vol forecast
    ML->>DB: Upsert predictions collection with new forecast

    Note over User,DB: Authentication
    User->>API: POST /auth/login with username and password
    API->>API: Verify credentials against stored hash
    API-->>User: Return access_token valid for 24 hours

    Note over User,DB: Authenticated data request
    User->>API: GET /api/predictions  coin=bitcoin  horizon=7
    API->>API: Verify JWT signature and check expiry
    API->>DB: Query predictions sorted by created_at descending
    DB-->>API: Return latest prediction document
    API-->>User: Return prices, volatility, direction arrays for 7 days

    Note over User,API: Token expiry — handled by Axios response interceptor
    User->>API: GET /api/prices/realtime with expired token
    API-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
    User->>API: POST /auth/refresh with refresh_token
    API-->>User: Return new access_token
    User->>API: Retry GET /api/prices/realtime with new token
    API->>DB: Query realtime_prices sorted by event_time desc  limit 100
    DB-->>API: Return price records with technical indicators
    API-->>User: Return JSON array to update RealtimePage chart
